also and the previous one as well.

18
00:02:49,145 --> 00:02:54,445
Plumbers, plumbers, plumbers, plumbers, plumbers, plumbers, plumbers, plumbers,

19
00:02:54,585 --> 00:02:54,635
plumbers.

20
